graph LR
    ODHModelController[ODH Model Controller<br/>v1.27.0-rhods-453]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ODHModelController -->|orchestration| Kubernetes[Kubernetes v1.28+]
    ODHModelController -->|CRD provider| KServe[KServe v0.12.1]
    ODHModelController -->|Route API| OpenShift[OpenShift v4.x]
    ODHModelController -->|webhook certs| CertMgr[cert-manager /<br/>service-ca-operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Conditional - Service Mesh)
    ODHModelController -.->|if mesh enabled| Istio[Istio/Maistra v1.19+]
    ODHModelController -.->|if serverless mode| Knative[Knative Serving v0.39.3]
    ODHModelController -.->|if mesh enabled| Authorino[Authorino v0.15.0]
    ODHModelController -.->|if monitoring NS set| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.64.1+]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ODHModelController -->|reads config| ODHOperator[opendatahub-operator<br/>DataScienceCluster/DSCInit]
    ODHModelController -.->|coordinates with| KServeController[kserve-controller]
    ODHModelController -.->|if flag enabled| ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
    ODHModelController -.->|mesh config| ServiceMeshCP[Service Mesh<br/>Control Plane]
    ODHModelController -->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus]

    %% Integration Points (External)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| ODHModelController
    Pipelines[Data Science<br/>Pipelines] -.->|auto-deployment| ODHModelController

    %% External Services
    ODHModelController -.->|monitoring| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>Server]
    K8sAPI -->|provides| Kubernetes

    %% Watched CRDs (from dependencies)
    KServe -->|provides| InferenceServiceCRD[InferenceService CRD<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
    KServe -->|provides| ServingRuntimeCRD[ServingRuntime CRD<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    Istio -->|provides| IstioCRDs[VirtualService,<br/>Gateway, PeerAuth,<br/>Telemetry CRDs]
    Authorino -->|provides| AuthConfigCRD[AuthConfig CRD<br/>authorino.kuadrant.io]
    OpenShift -->|provides| RouteCRD[Route CRD<br/>route.openshift.io/v1]
    PrometheusOp -->|provides| MonitoringCRDs[ServiceMonitor,<br/>PodMonitor CRDs]
    ServiceMeshCP -->|provides| MaistraCRDs[ServiceMeshMember,<br/>ServiceMeshMemberRoll CRDs]
    Knative -->|provides| KnativeServiceCRD[Knative Service CRD<br/>serving.knative.dev/v1]

    ODHModelController -->|watches| InferenceServiceCRD
    ODHModelController -->|creates/watches| ServingRuntimeCRD
    ODHModelController -->|creates| IstioCRDs
    ODHModelController -->|creates| AuthConfigCRD
    ODHModelController -->|creates| RouteCRD
    ODHModelController -->|creates| MonitoringCRDs
    ODHModelController -->|creates| MaistraCRDs
    ODHModelController -->|validates| KnativeServiceCRD

